---
description: Grug map rules v1
alwaysApply: true
---
- Grug Map: Look at folder names first. Do not scan file contents to find "where things are."
- Core Paths: Logic is in src/ (services/controllers). Tests are in test/.
- Surgical Context: Only read files for the specific module being discussed.
- Ignore Junk: Never look at dist/ or node_modules/.
- Manual: Use @Files for direct edits; avoid @Codebase unless lost.
